body:
1 IssueIOU Transaction   Go to Apps Tab &gt; Create to create a new Application &ldquo;IOU&rdquo;
  Create a flow
 flow name &ldquo;IssueIOU&rdquo; &gt; Add a trigger, select &ldquo;SmartContract Action Trigger&rdquo; from the list  Select &ldquo;IOU&rdquo; from the dropdown menu Click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; and &ldquo;Next&rdquo; to get to &ldquo;Define Transaction Input&rdquo; section, security and time window are not supported for Corda smart contract Add input fields  linearId, select &ldquo;LinearId&rdquo; from type dropdown menu issuer, select &ldquo;Party&rdquo; from type dropdown menu holder, select &ldquo;Party&rdquo; from type dropdown menu amt, select &ldquo;Amount&rdquo; from type dropdown menu click &ldquo;Next&rdquo;   Add output fields, leave this blank, click &ldquo;Continue&rdquo; Select &ldquo;Copy Schema&rdquo;   Select the trigger  Map to flow inputs   Now we will implement the flow  Add &ldquo;Ledger Operation&rdquo; activity from Dovetail-Ledger category Map input      2 TransferIOU Transaction  Create a new flow to implement TransferIOU transaction  Add a trigger, select &ldquo;SmartContract Action Trigger&rdquo; from the list  Select &ldquo;IOU&rdquo; from the dropdown menu Click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; and &ldquo;Next&rdquo; to get to &ldquo;Define Transaction Input&rdquo; section, security and time window are not supported for Corda smart contract Add input fields  iou, select &ldquo;AssetRef&rdquo; from Type dropdown menu, enter &ldquo;com.example.iou.IOU&rdquo; in the RecordType field, select &ldquo;True&rdquo; from Consuming dropdown menu newHolder, select &ldquo;Party&rdquo; from type dropdown menu click &ldquo;Next&rdquo;   Add output fields, leave this blank, click &ldquo;Continue&rdquo; Select &ldquo;Copy Schema&rdquo;   Select the trigger  Map to flow inputs   Now we will implement the flow  Add &ldquo;Ledger Operation&rdquo; activity from Dovetail-Ledger category Map input      3 SettleIOU Transaction  Create a new flow to implement SettleIOU transaction  Add a trigger, select &ldquo;SmartContract Action Trigger&rdquo; from the list * Select &ldquo;IOU&rdquo; from the dropdown menu * Click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; and &ldquo;Next&rdquo; to get to &ldquo;Define Transaction Input&rdquo; section, security and time window are not supported for Corda smart contract * Add input fields * iou, select &ldquo;AssetRef&rdquo; from Type dropdown menu, enter &ldquo;com.example.iou.IOU&rdquo; in the RecordType field, select &ldquo;True&rdquo; from Consuming dropdown menu * funds, select &ldquo;AssetRef&rdquo; from Type dropdown menu, select &ldquo;True&rdquo; from Consuming dropdown menu, select &ldquo;True&rdquo; from Repeating dropdown menu * click &ldquo;Next&rdquo; * Add output fields, leave this blank, click &ldquo;Continue&rdquo; * Select &ldquo;Copy Schema&rdquo;  Select the trigger  Map to flow inputs   Now we will implement the flow  Add &ldquo;Payment Processor&rdquo; activity from Dovetail-Ledger category Map input
